194
00:14:46,741 --> 00:14:48,141
Omong apa sih kau?

195
00:14:48,210 --> 00:14:50,210
Ini berlian.

196
00:14:50,210 --> 00:14:52,050
Kualitas terbaik.

197
00:14:52,550 --> 00:14:54,981
Sebutannya <i>White Star</i>.

198
00:14:55,351 --> 00:14:57,151
Harganya 200 milyar.

199
00:14:57,521 --> 00:14:58,991
